@startuml
title Feature 032 - admin WMS/1C, stocks, warehouses and supplies

actor "Логистический администратор" as LogisticAdmin
actor "Складской оператор" as WarehouseOperator
actor "Оператор интеграции WMS/1C" as IntegrationOperator
participant "Admin frontend\n/admin/wms" as AdminUi
participant "admin-wms API\n/module admin-wms" as AdminWms
database "admin_wms_*" as WmsDb
participant "admin-pim API\npublished products" as AdminPim
participant "admin-catalog API\ncatalog periods" as AdminCatalog
participant "order/checkout workflow" as OrderFlow
participant "partner-office workflow" as PartnerOffice
participant "WMS/1C external systems" as WmsOneC
participant "Audit trail" as Audit

LogisticAdmin -> AdminUi: открывает список складов и остатков
AdminUi -> AdminWms: GET /warehouses, GET /stocks
AdminWms -> WmsDb: search warehouses and stock snapshots
WmsDb --> AdminWms: pages
AdminWms --> AdminUi: WarehousePage, StockPage

LogisticAdmin -> AdminUi: меняет availability policy SKU
AdminUi -> AdminWms: POST /stocks/{stockItemId}/availability-rule
AdminWms -> AdminPim: validate SKU is published
AdminPim --> AdminWms: product published
AdminWms -> AdminCatalog: validate catalog period and channel
AdminCatalog --> AdminWms: period valid
AdminWms -> WmsDb: update availability rule and stock snapshot
AdminWms -> Audit: ADMIN_WMS_AVAILABILITY_CHANGED
AdminWms --> AdminUi: StockResponse with mnemonic result

WarehouseOperator -> AdminUi: создает поставку и начинает приемку
AdminUi -> AdminWms: POST /supplies with Idempotency-Key
AdminWms -> WmsDb: insert supply and lines
AdminWms -> Audit: ADMIN_WMS_SUPPLY_CREATED
AdminWms --> AdminUi: SupplyResponse
WarehouseOperator -> AdminUi: подтверждает приемку строк
AdminUi -> AdminWms: POST /supplies/{id}/acceptance with Idempotency-Key
AdminWms -> WmsDb: check idempotency and current supply status
alt repeated idempotency key
  AdminWms --> AdminUi: existing SupplyResponse without duplicate movement
else first acceptance
  AdminWms -> WmsDb: insert stock movements, update stock snapshots, create discrepancies
  AdminWms -> PartnerOffice: publish supply acceptance context
  AdminWms -> Audit: ADMIN_WMS_SUPPLY_ACCEPTED
  AdminWms --> AdminUi: SupplyResponse(ACCEPTED or PARTIALLY_ACCEPTED)
end

OrderFlow -> AdminWms: POST /reservations with order id and SKU
AdminWms -> WmsDb: lock stock row and validate sellable quantity
alt enough stock
  AdminWms -> WmsDb: create reservation, decrement sellable, increment reserved
  AdminWms -> Audit: ADMIN_WMS_RESERVATION_HELD
  AdminWms --> OrderFlow: ReservationResponse(HELD)
else not enough stock
  AdminWms --> OrderFlow: 409 STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_WMS_STOCK_NOT_ENOUGH with available quantity
end
OrderFlow -> AdminWms: POST /reservations/{id}/release
AdminWms -> WmsDb: release once by idempotency key
AdminWms -> Audit: ADMIN_WMS_RESERVATION_RELEASED
AdminWms --> OrderFlow: ReservationResponse(RELEASED)

IntegrationOperator -> AdminUi: запускает ручную синхронизацию
AdminUi -> AdminWms: POST /sync-runs with Idempotency-Key
AdminWms -> WmsDb: create sync run STARTED
AdminWms -> WmsOneC: request stock/supply documents
WmsOneC --> AdminWms: messages with externalDocumentId and idempotencyKey
loop each message
  AdminWms -> WmsDb: check sourceSystem + externalDocumentId + externalLineId + idempotencyKey
  alt duplicate
    AdminWms -> WmsDb: mark DUPLICATE_IGNORED
  else conflict with confirmed movement
    AdminWms -> WmsDb: store sync message QUARANTINED
    AdminWms -> Audit: ADMIN_WMS_SYNC_QUARANTINED
  else valid message
    AdminWms -> WmsDb: apply movement or supply update
    AdminWms -> Audit: ADMIN_WMS_SYNC_MESSAGE_PROCESSED
  end
end
AdminWms -> WmsDb: finish sync run counters
AdminWms --> AdminUi: SyncRunResponse with counters

@enduml
